{"tid":632634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警涉荃灣偷40元貨品 被控盜竊月底提堂","createTime":"2018-04-17T14:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T03:16:33.000Z","uid":54870,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"eb5fa42c326c7ccde6317f30f7562399f2d403df","tid":632634,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T14:41:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1188972/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1188972%2F&d=kJKF5bKJ3bb1eMIg7r1iL9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b518edfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1188972%2F&h=41655372\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1188972/</a><br />\n<br />\n即時新聞港聞<br />\n<br />\n選擇分類&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n休班警涉荃灣偷40元貨品 被控盜竊月底提堂<br />\n<br />\n2018-04-12 22:44&nbsp;文字大小<br />\n<br />\n1/1愉景新城。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n一名休班警員涉嫌上月14日荃灣盜竊40元貨品，警方今日落案控告一項「盜竊」罪，案件將於4月26日在西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n愉景新城商戶保安上月14日下午5時報案，指54歲姓沈男休班警員盜去一件貨品，價值約40元。新界南總區重案組人員接手調查案件，休班警涉嫌店鋪盜竊被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方證實被捕男子為一名警務人員。警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n40蚊都偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ffc7519ef834db7db2ffc3c1cc6bff98ca11fe","tid":632634,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb5fa42c326c7ccde6317f30f7562399f2d403df","tid":632634,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T14:41:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1188972/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1188972%2F&d=kJKF5bKJ3bb1eMIg7r1iL9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b518